~( ^.x.^)>
Timer function. Takes a callback function
and returns the elapsed time.
<(^.x.^ )~

=^.x.^= timer(fn)
    mew start = time()
    fn()
    bring time_info(time() - start)
meow meow


~( ^.x.^)>
Time conversion functions.
<(^.x.^ )~

=^.x.^= time_info(x)
    mew min = floor(x / 60)
    mew sec = floor(x % 60)
    mew msec = (x % 1) * 1000
    bring =^.x.^= [
        min: min,
        sec: sec,
        msec: msec
    ]
meow meow



